{"tid":234133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法國大選] 馬克龍當選法最年輕總統 得票率66%大勝馬琳勒龐","createTime":"2017-05-08T04:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T05:54:23.000Z","uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d47daef76e6b70850c59ebf6f3f0c8d2ed0e32f","tid":234133,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/125530_d3a8d2b42f60271d6e61d5c48636cba3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F125530_d3a8d2b42f60271d6e61d5c48636cba3.jpg&h=24342e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國周日舉行總統大選第二輪投票，全國6.7萬個票站由香港時間昨午2時起開放，直至凌晨2時結束投票。點票結果顯示，中間派候選人、年僅39歲的馬克龍（Emmanuel Macron）得票率66.06%，擊敗得票率僅33.94%的極右馬琳勒龐（Marine Le Pen），成為法國自拿破崙時代以來最年輕總統。<br />\n<br />\n票站調查結果公佈後，總理卡澤納夫（Bernard Cazeneuve）說選民選了馬克龍為總統。馬克龍向傳媒表示，法國揭開「充滿希望和信心的新一頁」。他其後發表演說，表示會修補國家分化。<br />\n<br />\n數以千計馬克龍支持者在巴黎羅浮宮外集會慶祝，揮舞法國國旗。有人說馬克龍象徵希望，猶如2008年當選美國總統的奧巴馬。馬克龍到場發表勝利宣言，說當務之急是重新令歐洲團結、改善經濟、防範極端主義威脅。<br />\n<br />\n馬琳勒龐承認落敗，致電祝賀馬克龍當選，指選民支持維持現狀。<br />\n<br />\n將要交棒的現任總統奧朗德，說大部份選民希望在「共和國價值」下團結一致。<br />\n<br />\n選舉投票率為65.3%，低於2012年同期的71.96%。票站調查顯示，今次選舉白票和廢票率創新高，在已點算的70%選票中，白票和廢票佔了12.1%。「棄權」選民比例亦是近50年來最高，超過25%。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍勝出，法國脫歐風險消除，亞洲匯市早盤歐元兌美元匯率由1.0998升至1.1023，是半年來新高。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170508&amp;guid=56662591&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170508%26guid%3D56662591%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=61a25200\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170508%26guid%3D56662591%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=39f82643\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170508&amp;guid=56662591&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"a4450f37c5925bd59f74eec979ef844cb631a51e","tid":234133,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"Le pen<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03991d593ce494783b7abdb2f5e3a788b6c95615","tid":234133,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"英美右翼又豬 歐盟又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0bfb103b4fdb3fa249a1dca69c5cff364f1c1c","tid":234133,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"一見到佢就諗起佢老婆6x歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a52793dfbbd7c327e5b476f10c02e7dd4a0c3af","tid":234133,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"Isis機會黎喇"},{"pid":"3fcec09047f2454f02a93b325b1ced5d9b0fe9f0","tid":234133,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"法國玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,成個歐洲除左大英祖國之外全部伊斯蘭化30年後白人滅絕"},{"pid":"7a763896360f7af68cbbccef7d6245641c68a7c2","tid":234133,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6411ce8af0173fb128df2045f153c5c8182c33c4","tid":234133,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:24:34.000Z","msg":"allahu akbar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82f0876a2af03639179276000a43f4174d9c112","tid":234133,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒山又中</blockquote><br />\n燒山真是破燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.